Class MoveChecker

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.ingsw.GC_32.Server.Game.MoveChecker

  • public class MoveChecker
extends java.lang.Object
    the main clas which perform the simulation of the action and assess if the action is valid or not.
    • cloner: instance of the cloner which is used for copy the elements of the game, in particular the board, the action and the player status
